%N A394583 Numbers k such that the k-th Stieltjes constant is positive.
%C A394583 In other words, numbers k such that the coefficient of s^k in the expansion of zeta(1-s) is positive, where zeta is the Riemann zeta function.
%C A394583 Union of {0} and [A354835(2*m)+1, A354835(2*m+1)] for all m >= 1.
%H A394583 Jianing Song, <a href="/A394583/b394583.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10013</a> (all terms up to A354835(1580) = 20009)
%H A394583 Krzysztof Maślanka, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2210.07244">Asymptotic Properties of Stieltjes Constants</a>, arXiv:2210.07244 [math.NT], 2022.
%H A394583 Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, <a href="https://mathworld.wolfram.com/StieltjesConstants.html">Stieltjes Constants</a>.
%H A394583 Wikipedia, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stieltjes_constants">Stieltjes constants</a>.
%t A394583 Select[Range[0, 150], StieltjesGamma[#] > 0 &] (* _Paolo Xausa_, May 22 2026 *)
%Y A394583 Cf. A114523 (signs of Stieltjes constants), A354835. A395455 is the complement.
